iata:ULDtype.description: Code identifying a standard Unit Load Device type

iata:ULDataDesignator.description: Code identifying US/ATA Unit Load Device type

iata:ULDownerCode.description: Code to identify the owner of a Unit Load Device (Actual format is aa, an or na. Owner can be an airline or leasing company.)

iata:ULDloadingIndicator.description: Code indicating ULD height or loading limitation

iata:ULDtareWeight.description: Indicates the weight of the transport equipment used
